<p><strong>Skills</strong> Perception +3</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1/8 (25 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Keen Hearing and Smell.</em></strong> The mastiff has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on hearing or smell.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Bite.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +3 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 4 (1d6 + 1) piercing damage. If the target is a creature, it must succeed on a DC 11 Strength saving throw or be knocked prone.</p>

